172 A.3d 1084 STATE OF NEW JERSEY, PLAINTIFF-RESPONDENT, v. BRIAN M. RICHARDSON, DEFENDANT-PETITIONER.

C-278 September Term 2017

079004 November 9, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-003619-13 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
